ck=\"key=www_unlogin_home&value=hot01\">\n            <div class=\"pic W_piccut_v\">\n                <a href=\"\/a\/hot\/88bef4745430d526_0.html?type=grap\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https:\/\/ww4.sinaimg.cn\/thumb180\/0066Nb6jly1g9ln50pgexj30hg169nby.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/a>\n            <\/div>\n            <div class=\"list_des\">\n                <h3 class=\"list_title_s\"><a href=\"\/a\/hot\/88bef4745430d526_0.html?type=grap\" class=\"S_txt1\" target=\"_blank\">#高以翔妈妈#<\/a><\/h3>\n                <div class=\"des_main S_txt2\">高以翔妈妈请的法师称，“高以翔放不下，一直不肯走。那个天使高以翔抱着自己的遗体轻轻抚摸，仿佛不舍跟与他共存35年的身体分开。”\n每日一问，蓝台今天道歉了嘛？\n#高以翔妈妈# #高以翔曾在电影中饰演吉喆# ​​​​<\/div>\n            <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n                <div class=\"UG_list_c\" action-type=\"feed_list_item\" href=\"\/a\/hot\/c9941066c7669ccb_0.html?type=grap\" suda-uatrack=\"key=www_unlogin_home&value=hot02\">\n            <div class=\"pic W_piccut_v\">\n                <a href=\"\/a\/hot\/c9941066c7669ccb_0.html?type=grap\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https:\/\/ww4.sinaimg.cn\/thumb180\/67972e52ly1g9ljyzy63dj20c20e7mxh.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/a>\n            <\/div>\n            <div class=\"list_des\">\n                <h3 class=\"list_title_s\"><a href=\"\/a\/hot\/c9941066c7669ccb_0.html?type=grap\" class=\"S_txt1\" target=\"_blank\">#吉喆去世#<\/a><\/h3>\n                <div class=\"des_main S_txt2\">年仅33岁的前CBA球员吉喆因肺癌去世[蜡烛]\n吉喆，1986年10月14日出生于辽宁沈阳，司职大前锋，效力于北京首钢篮球俱乐部。\n2005年，吉喆带领东北大学获得第二届CUBS联赛冠军。2006年，吉喆代表中国参加NIKE世界篮球峰会。2007年，吉喆被辽宁男篮租借至北京首钢队征战CBA。2012年，吉喆永久转会北京队。 ​​​​<\/div>\n            <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n                <div class=\"UG_list_c\" action-type=\"feed_list_item\" href=\"\/a\/hot\/64e60990282ad6d4_0.html?type=grap\" suda-uatrack=\"key=www_unlogin_home&value=hot03\">\n            <div class=\"pic W_piccut_v\">\n                <a href=\"\/a\/hot\/64e60990282ad6d4_0.html?type=grap\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https:\/\/imgaliyuncdn.miaopai.com\/images\/GUk19hMvZM37hcRIll~m5jOxtg-wm~gdNW8PmA___j1lx_4.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/a>\n            <\/div>\n            <div class=\"list_des\">\n                <h3 class=\"list_title_s\"><a href=\"\/a\/hot\/64e60990282ad6d4_0.html?type=grap\" class=\"S_txt1\" target=\"_blank\">#高以翔曾在电影中饰演吉喆#<\/a><\/h3>\n                <div class=\"des_main S_txt2\">【痛惜！#高以翔曾在电影中饰演吉喆#，2人离世仅隔8天[泪]】今天，前CBA北京首钢球员焦健透露，北京男篮夺冠功臣#吉喆#医治无效不幸去世，年仅33岁。2017年上映的电影《我是马布里》中，高以翔扮演的角色杨西亚原型便是吉喆，而两人去世相差仅仅8天。 愿天堂还有篮球和爱陪伴。http:\/\/t.cn\/AieLEwFc ​​​​<\/div>\n            <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n                <div class=\"UG_list_c\" action-type=\"feed_list_item\" href=\"\/a\/hot\/57cc2c5ca618c658_0.html?type=grap\" suda-uatrack=\"key=www_unlogin_home&value=hot04\">\n            <div class=\"pic W_piccut_v\">\n                <a href=\"\/a\/hot\/57cc2c5ca618c658_0.html?type=grap\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https:\/\/ww4.sinaimg.cn\/thumb180\/006Rnuyvgy1g9lm3zwsxbj30j60nqwgm.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/a>\n            <\/div>\n            <div class=\"list_des\">\n                <h3 class=\"list_title_s\"><a href=\"\/a\/hot\/57cc2c5ca618c658_0.html?type=grap\" class=\"S_txt1\" target=\"_blank\">#石头姐订婚#<\/a><\/h3>\n                <div class=\"des_main S_txt2\">#石头姐订婚#恭喜石头姐！！今天也是为别人甜甜爱情🍋的一天 ​​​​<\/div>\n            <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n                <div class=\"UG_list_c\" action-type=\"feed_list_item\" href=\"\/a\/hot\/6ae31df42289e690_0.html?type=grap\" suda-uatrack=\"key=www_unlogin_home&value=hot05\">\n            <div class=\"pic W_piccut_v\">\n                <a href=\"\/a\/hot\/6ae31df42289e690_0.html?type=grap\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https:\/\/ww4.sinaimg.cn\/thumb180\/c0cb4ebaly1g9ln76n0hjg20k00il4qt.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/a>\n            <\/div>\n            <div class=\"list_des\">\n                <h3 class=\"list_title_s\"><a href=\"\/a\/hot\/6ae31df42289e690_0.html?type=grap\" class=\"S_txt1\" target=\"_blank\">#脸长的好看有多重要#<\/a><\/h3>\n                <div class=\"des_main S_txt2\">#脸长的好看有多重要#\n\n不止颜值高 看了张艺兴的微真人秀《归零》\n跟随他的脚步见识了世界的精彩 去直面真实的自己 并且持续探索 开坦克 冲浪 在大海上肆意 在马路上狂奔 和不同的人合作音乐 没有精致妆容西装革履 整个人恣意快活的张艺兴 真的是无比有魅力😭 ​​​​<\/div>\n            <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n    <div class=\"UG_box_foot\">\n        <a href=\"\/\/weibo.com\/a\/hot\/realtime\" class=\"S_txt1\" target=\"_blank\">查看更多<i class=\"W_ficon ficon_arrow_right S_ficon\">a<\/i><\/a>\n    <\/div>\n<\/div>\n"})</script>
